snippet.title: Sonic Jam Game.Com Remake Demo V2 Release Trailer.
snippet.description:
I am exited to announce that Sonic Jam game.com remake's SAGE 2024 demo has been updated!
The update includes:
Bug fixes
Act 2 of the Sonic 2 portion
The first Boss
and More!!!

Get the game here: 
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-jam-game-com-remake.2261/
